values.content:
=Client Qualification Scoring

Details:
Name: {{ $json.fields.Name }}
Email: {{ $json.fields.Email }}
Company: {{ $json.fields.Company }}
Service Needed: {{ $json.fields['Service Needed'] }}
Phone: {{ $json.fields['Phone '] }}

Give me:
1. A score from 1 to 10 on how valuable or likely this client is to convert.
2. One line reason for this score.

Respond in this JSON format:
{
  "score": number,
  "reason": "string"
}

parameters.jsCode:
// Assuming only one item is passed
const item = items[0];

// Parse OpenAI response
const response = JSON.parse(item.json.message.content);

// Return the combined object
return [
  {
    json: {
      // previous client details
      airtableId: item.json.airtableId || item.json.id, 
      name: item.json["Client Name"],
      email: item.json["Client Email"],
      company: item.json["Company"],
      service: item.json["Service Needed"],
      phone: item.json["Phone"],


      // AI scoring
      id: response.id,
      score: response.score,
      reason: response.reason
    }
  }
];

